- *Loss Aggregation*: Assessing accumulation exposure across multiple cedants and geographies
- *Model Development*: Building proprietary models for perils not well-captured by vendors (e.g., Australian inland flooding, bushfire)
- *Validation*: Back-testing model performance against actual catastrophe events
- *Climate Change Analysis*: Incorporating climate science into forward-looking risk assessments

